# AI Task Execution Guide

## Before Starting

### 1. Understand the Task
- Confirm instructions received
- Summarize main tasks
- Identify key requirements

### 2. Check for Existing Code
- Search for similar functionality
- Check for duplicate components
- Find reusable patterns

### 3. Review Project Rules
- Read `_core-rules.mdc` (always applied)
- Check relevant guides (architecture, state, etc.)
- Note tech stack constraints

