## Implementation Guidelines

### Follow Clean Architecture

```
features/<feature>/
â”śâ”€â”€ data/        # DTOs, Repositories
â”śâ”€â”€ domain/      # Use cases, Domain models
â””â”€â”€ presentation/ # Screens, Providers, Widgets
```

### Use Existing Patterns

| For | Use |
|-----|-----|
| State management | `BaseNotifier<T>` or `PaginatedNotifier<T>` |
| Pull-to-refresh | `RefreshableContent<T>` or `PaginatedListView<T>` |
| Error handling | `Result` pattern with `Success`/`Failure` |
| State classes | Freezed sealed unions |
| API enums | `EnumClass` with `wireName`/`wireNumber` |
| Async providers | `FutureProvider` for services/repositories |
| Notifier with async deps | Pass `Ref` to notifier constructor |
| Local storage | `SharedPreferences` via `sharedPreferencesProvider` |
| Settings persistence | Repository with JSON encode/decode |
| Cards/containers | `CardContainer`, `DashboardCard` |
| Buttons | `PrimaryButton` |
| Inputs | `InputField` |
| Status display | `StatusBadge`, `StatItem` |
| Loading spinners | `SpinKitPulse` from flutter_spinkit |

### Naming Conventions

| Type | Convention | Example |
|------|------------|---------|
| Files | `snake_case` | `login_screen.dart` |
| Classes | `PascalCase` | `LoginScreen` |
| Variables | `camelCase` | `userName` |

